so A, Campo GM, Scordo MG, Caputi AP, Perucca E "Effect of ketoconazole on the pharmacokinetics of imipramine and desipramine in healthy subjects." Br J Clin Pharmacol 43 (1997): 315-8[4] Spina E, Avenoso A, Campo GM, Scordo MG, Caputi AP, Perucca E "Effect of ketoconazole on the pharmacokinetics of imipramine and desipramine in healthy subjects." Br J Clin Pharmacol 43 (1997): 315-8[5] Robinson RF, Nahata MC, Olshefski RS "Syncope associated with concurrent amitriptyline and fluconazole therapy." Ann Pharmacother 34 (2000): 1406-9[6] Newberry DL, Bass SN, Mbanefo CO "A fluconazole/amitriptyline drug interaction in three male adults." Clin Infect Dis 24 (1997): 270-1', 1767365207);
